* &quot;The Bible Code II: The Countdown&quot;. (US, Viking Books, 2002, ); (UK, Weidenfeld &amp; Nicolson, 2002, )
* &quot;The Bible Code III: The Quest&quot;. (UK, Weidenfeld &amp; Nicolson, 2010, )

==Related literature==
* Jeffrey Satinover: &quot;Cracking the Bible Code&quot;. Wm Morrow, 1997. . Appeared slightly later, follows a more historical and traditional route.

